{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Mimir/Prometheus metrics datasource",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    },
    {
      "name": "DS_LOKI",
      "label": "Loki",
      "description": "Loki logs datasource",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "loki",
      "pluginName": "Loki"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "10.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "loki",
      "name": "Loki",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "timeseries",
      "name": "Time series",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "stat",
      "name": "Stat",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "logs",
      "name": "Logs",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "barchart",
      "name": "Bar chart",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "text",
      "name": "Text",
      "version": ""
    }
  ],
  "uid": "cantolico-api-overview",
  "title": "Cantólico — API Overview",
  "description": "Multi-source dashboard combining Loki logs, Mimir metrics, and Tempo trace links",
  "tags": ["cantolico", "api", "overview"],
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Traffic Overview",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Requests/min",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqpm"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{service_name=\"cantolico\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Requests/min",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate 5xx",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqpm"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_errors_total{service_name=\"cantolico\",error_class=\"5xx\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx Errors/min",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate 4xx",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "reqpm"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_errors_total{service_name=\"cantolico\",error_class=\"4xx\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "4xx Errors/min",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "P95 Latency (ms)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 1, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 500 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2000 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "ms",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_ms_bucket{service_name=\"cantolico\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "P95 Latency",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Logs",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 9, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "5xx Errors Rate",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate({app=\"cantolico\",level=\"error\",category=\"api\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx Error Rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "4xx Warnings Rate",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 10, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate({app=\"cantolico\",level=\"warn\",category=\"api\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "4xx Warning Rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Slow Requests",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 10, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 20 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "count_over_time({app=\"cantolico\"} | json | tags=~\".*slow-request.*\" [$__range])",
          "legendFormat": "Slow Requests",
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Unique Active Users",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 10, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "blue", "mode": "fixed" },
          "unit": "short",
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "count(count_over_time({app=\"cantolico\"} | json | user_email != \"\" [$__range]) by (user_email))",
          "legendFormat": "Active Users",
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "User Activity",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Recent API Requests Log",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 14, "h": 10 },
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": false
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "{app=\"cantolico\",category=\"api\"} | json | line_format \"{{.user_email}} {{.http_method}} {{.http_path}} \\u2192 {{.http_status_code}} ({{.http_response_time_ms}}ms)\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Top Paths by Error Count",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 14, "y": 19, "w": 10, "h": 10 },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "barWidth": 0.97,
        "barRadius": 0,
        "xTickLabelRotation": 0,
        "xTickLabelMaxLength": 30,
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" },
          "custom": {
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "lineWidth": 0
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "sum by (path) (count_over_time({app=\"cantolico\",level=\"error\",category=\"api\"} | json [$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{path}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Performance",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 29, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "P95 Latency by Path (Loki)",
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 30, "w": 18, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"] }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 5,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${DS_LOKI}" },
          "expr": "quantile_over_time(0.95, {app=\"cantolico\",category=\"api\"} | json | unwrap response_time_ms [5m]) by (path)",
          "legendFormat": "{{path}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Traces Explorer Link",
      "datasource": null,
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 30, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Distributed Traces\n\nExplore traces for the `cantolico` service in Tempo:\n\n**[Open Tempo Explorer](d/explore?left={\"datasource\":\"${DS_TEMPO}\",\"queries\":[{\"refId\":\"A\",\"datasource\":{\"type\":\"tempo\"},\"queryType\":\"traceql\",\"query\":\"{.service.name=\\\\\"cantolico\\\\\"}\"}]})**\n\n### Quick filters\n- Service: `cantolico`\n- High latency: filter by duration > 2s\n- Error traces: filter by status = error\n\n> Tip: Click any trace ID in the API logs to jump directly to the trace timeline."
      }
    }
  ]
}
